Content:
Sample config has 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3060] gotten an update
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3031] here
Some 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3052] README links got updated
More 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3013] README updates
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2996] here
README now shows 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2993] contributor icons
